Scenario name : Success Create Equipment Inspection Form

No.	      Test Step	                                                Expected Result
1	        Open the Hazard menu in Mobile App                        The Hazard page shows list of existing hazard reports
2	        Tap Report Hazard / New Hazard button                     App opens the Hazard Reporting Form
3	        Select Location (Mandatory)                               Dropdown opens, user can select 1 location; selected value appears
4	        Select Sublocation (Mandatory)                            Dropdown opens, user can select 1 sublocation; selected value appears
5	        Select Area (Mandatory)                                   Dropdown opens, user can select 1 area; selected value appears
6	        Input Area Description (Optional)                         Text field accepts input (can be left empty)
  7	        Tap Evidence – Image                                    Picker	Camera/Gallery opens
8	        Capture or choose an image                                Image preview added to Evidence field (mandatory fulfilled)
9	        Select PIC (Mandatory, Preselect to reporter)             PIC field is auto-filled with the reporter’s name
10	      Submit the Hazard report                                  Request is sent to server; system generates hazard entry and follow-up task
11	      PIC receives notification                                 PIC gets notification for the follow-up task
12	      All users in the same                                     Area receive hazard notification	Area users receive hazard alert notification
13	      PIC opens the                                             Follow-up Task assigned to them	Task details screen appears
14	      PIC visits location and opens                             Submit Follow-up	Follow-up submission form appears
15	      Add Evidence (Image Picker)                               Camera/Gallery opens to add proof image
16	      Select Resolution Date using DateTime Picker              DateTime picker opens; selected date/time appears correctly
17	      Add CoObserver by tapping (+) button                      System adds additional Select fields for more observers
18	      Select one or more Co Observers                           Observers appear as selected entries
19	      Submit the follow-up task                                 Follow-up is successfully submitted to the server
20	      Direct Supervisor of the Area receives notification       Supervisor gets notification indicating follow-up completion
